About YRF Spy Universe:
YRF Spy Universe is a first of its kind cinematic universe of spy thriller films in India. The first film in the universe, "Ek Tha Tiger", starring Salman Khan and Katrina Kaif was released in 2012, followed by its sequel "Tiger Zinda Hai" in 2017. The third film in the universe, "War" was released in 2019 and starred Hrithik Roshan and Tiger Shroff in pivotal roles. "Pathaan" was the fourth instalment in the Spy Universe franchise which was released in 2023 starring Shah Rukh Khan, Deepika Padukone and John Abraham. "Tiger 3", the fifth instalment in the YRF Spy Universe and the third film in the Tiger series, starring Salman Khan, Katrina Kaif and Emraan Hashmi, released in 2023. "War 2", the sixth film in the YRF Spy Universe, starring Hrithik Roshan, NTR and Kiara Advani, directed by Ayan Mukerji, released on 14 August 2025. "Alpha", the seventh film in the franchise and Hindi cinema’s first female-led YRF Spy Universe film, starring Alia Bhatt and Sharvari, will release on 25 December 2025.

ওপারে জবাব দেওয়ার নাই কি কোন ভয়...
যদি মন ভাঙ্গা আর মসজিদ ভাঙ্গা সমান হয়
তবে আখেরাতে বিচার হবে ক্ষমা নয়

হয়তো একদিন খুঁজবি আমায় এসে দেখবি আমি নাই
সেদিন আমি সাত আসমানে দেহ খানা খাটিয়াই
তুই বড় বেইমান পাখি দিয়া গেলি আমায় ফাঁকি
ওপারে জবাব দেওয়ার নাই কি কোন ভয়...
যদি মন ভাঙ্গা আর মসজিদ ভাঙ্গা সমান হয়
তবে আখেরাতে বিচার হবে ক্ষমা নয়

Banglish:
Tore mon pinjiray raikha chilam jotone
Tui khacha bhenge urli pakhi gopone
Tui boro beman pakhi diya geli amay faki
Opare jobab dewar nai ki kono bhoy...
Jodi mon bhanga ar mosjid bhanga soman hoy
Tobe akherate bichar hobe khoma noy

Antora: 1
Kotha chilo khor kutai bandhbo dujon sukher ghor
Seisob chilo mitthe asha lobher neshay korli por
Tui boro beman pakhi diya geli amay faki
Opare jobab dewar nai ki kono bhoy...
Jodi mon bhanga ar mosjid bhanga soman hoy
Tobe akherate bichar hobe khoma noy

Hoyto ekdin khujbi amay eshe dekhbi ami nai

Tui boro beman pakhi diya geli amay faki

You broke the cage and flew away secretly, oh bird

Then there will be judgment in the hereafter, not forgiveness

We were supposed to build a happy home with straws
All that was a false hope, you became a stranger in the intoxication of greed
You are a very treacherous bird, you deceived me

If breaking a heart and breaking a mosque are the same
Then there will be judgment in the hereafter, not forgiveness

Maybe one day you will look for me and see that I am not there
That day I will be in the seventh heaven, my body on a bier
You are a very treacherous bird, you deceived me
Aren't you afraid of answering on the other side...
If breaking a heart and breaking a mosque are the same
Then there will be judgment in the hereafter, not forgiveness

snippet.title: Dolphins Up Close with Bertie Gregory | Official Trailer | National Geographic
snippet.description:
Bertie Gregory heads to the Azores, a remote island chain in the Atlantic Ocean. Surrounded by Europe’s largest marine protected area, these waters are a vital stop for migrating predators, drawn here by rich feeding grounds. It’s the perfect time for Bertie to capture a rare natural spectacle—when elusive predators unite to hunt dense shoals of fish called bait balls. But with unpredictable storms, filming won’t be easy. During his journey, Bertie also explores the region’s dark history of marine exploitation. By meeting an ex-whaler turned whale spotter, he discovers how the end of whaling transformed the Azores into a sanctuary, allowing marine life to return and delicate food chains to thrive.

snippet.title: Alice In Borderland Season 3 | Official Trailer | Netflix
snippet.description:
The survival action series "Alice in Borderland" became the most watched Japanese Netflix title by worldwide audiences.

Now, the "games" that took the world by storm begin once again.

In the previous season, Arisu (#KentoYamazaki) and Usagi (#TaoTsuchiya) cleared all of the games and returned to the real world. They have since gotten married and established a happy life together. Their memories of the borderland were erased, but they see glimpses of it in dreams and hallucinations. One day, Usagi, led by afterlife researcher Ryuji (#KentoKaku), suddenly vanishes. At the same time as Usagi's disappearance, Banda (#HayatoIsomura) hands Arisu the final card: the Joker.

The uncharted journey led by the mysterious Joker card is about to unfold...

Season 3 of the Netflix Series "Alice in Borderland" is set for worldwide release on Thursday, September 25, 2025, only on Netflix.

#AliceinBorderlandS3, #AliceinBorderland3, #Netflix

Watch on Netflix: https://www.netflix.com/title/81682895

About Netflix:
Netflix is one of the world's leading entertainment services, with over 300 million paid memberships in over 190 countries enjoying TV series, films and games across a wide variety of genres and languages. Members can play, pause and resume watching as much as they want, anytime, anywhere, and can change their plans at any time.

Alice In Borderland Season 3 | Official Trailer | Netflix
https://www.youtube.com/@Netflix

When a morbid professor pulls Usagi back to Borderland, Arisu goes after her. But can he survive a new round of deadly games and escape the Joker's plans?
